A vintage 1980s-style product photography scene featuring a sleek smartphone encased in a chunky mechanical keyboard attachment, placed on a warm wood-grain desk surface. The composition includes scattered retro tech accessories: a coiled phone cord, a floppy disk, and a ceramic coffee mug with steam rising. Soft golden afternoon light streams through venetian blinds, casting dramatic striped shadows across the scene. The color palette features warm ambers, cream tones, and muted teals. Shot with shallow depth of field, the keyboard case is tack-sharp while the background fades into a pleasant bokeh. The aesthetic evokes nostalgic tech catalogs from the Sears or RadioShack era, celebrating the marriage of old-school tactile satisfaction with modern mobile technology.
